00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:56.980
Adam thinks deeply about
food I think it's safe to say

00:00:56.980 --> 00:01:01.340
and even better for his readers he
expresses his thoughts about food

00:01:01.340 --> 00:01:08.220
with a rare combination of wit,
sensitivity, emotion and logic.

00:01:08.220 --> 00:01:10.340
Here are a few lines from
The Table Comes First

00:01:10.340 --> 00:01:13.000
that might give you an idea
if you don't have one already

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:17.030
