00:01:35.060 --> 00:01:38.440
We alone know our fun.

00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:40.040
The sweetness in our
morning coffee is

00:01:40.040 --> 00:01:44.350
at once a feeling,
an idea and a memory.

00:01:44.350 --> 00:01:46.510
Ladies and gentlemen, please
welcome to the stage Adam Gopnik.

