have noticed this, right?

00:03:03.980 --> 00:03:07.590
And it's always the same
argument over and over again.

00:03:07.590 --> 00:03:12.770
I had my Uncle Ron and
my Aunt Rose who lived

00:03:12.770 --> 00:03:15.060
like all elderly Jewish
people in Florida.

00:03:15.060 --> 00:03:18.590
It's a law they were sent
